<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Bella Varelis is widely rumoured to be one of Locky Gilbert's finalists on The Bachelor.</p>

<p>And her outfit on Wednesday night's episode certainly won't do anything to dispel the rumours, with the 25-year-old opting for a racy designer wedding gown.  </p>

<p>Posting to Instagram, the reality star gave suffered a wardrobe malfunction in the very revealing dress ahead of hometown episodes. </p>

<p>Lady in white: In Wednesday night's episode Bella Varelis is set to wear a sheer designer wedding gown</p>

<p>In the photo, Bella looks glamorous in a white lacy dress that features a sheer skirt and intricate beading. </p>

<p>Her hair is loose in soft curls and she has a full face of makeup including pink eyeshow and a pink pout. </p>

<p>The showstopping dress is the 'Le Claudel' gown by bridal and red carpet label J.Andreatta. </p>

<p>Frontrunner: Bella is widely rumoured to be one of Locky Gilbert's finalists on The Bachelor and her dress won't do much to dispel them</p>

<p>The line was launched by Sydney-based designer Jessica Andreatta in 2018.  </p>

<p>According to the Queensland Times one of the designer gowns will set you back anywhere between $8000- $25,000.  </p>

<p>Bella's post comes ahead of the highly anticipated hometown visits, which will see Locky grilled by Bella's protective father. </p>

<p>Meeting the family: Bella's post comes ahead of the highly anticipated hometown visits, which will see Locky grilled by Bella's protective father</p>

<p>Posting alongside the picture, Bella revealed that the former Survivor star was very well prepared to meet her father. </p>

<p>'Locky learned to deal with high-pressure situations on survivor,' she wrote.</p>

<p>'Who knew that would be gearing him up to meet a protective Greek dad. p.s. dad is actually a big softie.' </p>

<p>The Bachelor continues Wednesday 7:30pm on Channel 10.  </p>

<p>Ready: Posting alongside the picture, Bella revealed that the former Survivor star (pictured) was very well prepared to meet her father</p>
